<p class= "section">A Collect for the Eve of Worship (Saturday)</p>
<p class= "default">O God, the source of eternal light: Shed forth your unending day
upon us who watch for you, that our lips may praise you, our lives
may bless you, and our worship on the morrow give you glory;
through Jesus Christ our Lord.
<span class= "italic"> Amen.</span></p>